      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a bit vague for me. I'm specifically asking about the recent $1M fund that I helped seed. I need hard numbers, not \"general information\" about other NGOs. For the $1M in South Sudan, what was the actual percentage that went into field aid versus the administrative/marketing side?",
